{"tid":448674,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[直播] 泰王國葬火化儀式","createTime":"2017-10-26T12:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T14:04:09.000Z","uid":24168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d56f7b66c8c12efb638c0f406a30c4196b304257","tid":448674,"uid":24168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:11:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eD7fgAzzVk8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeD7fgAzzVk8&d=zlQSdwqrDzpYYHyGoHHUOgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=2746b941\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eD7fgAzzVk8</a><br />\n<br />\n火葬場的中心是一座50公尺高象徵「須彌山」的火葬亭，蒲密蓬遺體將在此火化。須彌山為佛教、印度教和耆那所謂的宇宙中心。<br />\n<br />\n這座金色主亭飾有數十種與佛教和印度教有關的動物、神祇及神話生物精緻雕刻。最重要的位置將有蒲密蓬愛犬雕像。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夜幕低垂時，哇集拉隆功和其他王室成員將率先獻上檀木花。<br />\n<br />\n火化儀式將於晚間10時舉行（香港時間晚間11時），哇集拉隆功將主持點火。"},{"pid":"9f415313ac2ad0de2dccda76f8e4060840b3f44b","tid":448674,"uid":24168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:13:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BZbKXEc8uPs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBZbKXEc8uPs&d=zlQSdwqrDzpYYHyGoHHUOgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1f298a03\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BZbKXEc8uPs</a>"},{"pid":"a6320d99aeb5e1a251f0c5208b9248a223006619","tid":448674,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:04:09.000Z","msg":"幾時先肯燒嫁"}]}